Privacy
Perfect Company Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy was last modified on December 13, 2015.
Scope of this Privacy Statement
This Privacy Policy (this "Policy") discloses the privacy practices for Perfect Company (“Perfect Company”, "us" or "we") with respect to its websites, mobile applications and various related services (collectively, the "Services") and through other interactions and communications you have with us.  This Policy applies only to the information we collect through the Services. By using any of our Services, you agree that this Policy governs your use of our Services and any dispute concerning the Services. Please take a few minutes to read them before using or registering to access our Services.
