Collection of Information from Children
We comply with the Children's Online Privacy Protection Act, which requires us to notify and obtain consent from a parent or guardian before we collect, use and disclose the personal information of anyone under 13 years of age. We won't knowingly allow anyone under the age of 13 to provide us any personally identifying information online. If you're under 13, please do not register for any of our Services or provide us with any personally identifying information (such as your name, email address or phone number).
