Use of Information
We may use the information we collect about you to:
Personalize and improve the Services: including to provide or recommend features, content, social connections, referrals, and advertisements.
Perform Statistical Analysis:  We perform statistical, demographic and marketing analyses of users of the Perfect Company Services, and their usage patterns, for product development purposes, including analysis to troubleshoot software bugs and operational problems; to conduct data analysis, testing, and research; and to monitor and analyze usage and activity trends;
Provide, maintain, and improve our Services, including, for example, to facilitate payments, send receipts, provide products and services you request (and send related information), develop new features, and provide customer support.
Send you communications we think will be of interest to you:  Perfect company may periodically send communications including information about products, services, promotions, news, and events of Perfect Company and other companies, where permissible and according to local applicable laws; and to process contest, sweepstake, or other promotion entries and fulfill any related awards;
